{"tid":1540254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個政府根本無進步過","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:12:10.000Z","uid":127333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e41ca118933d81ea1abd0dff4248a5fd2e62b23f","tid":1540254,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:07:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭口口聲聲話要令社會前進<br />\n所以提出四大行動<br />\n但呢個政府自己都無前進過<br />\n仲想令社會向前行？<br />\n<br />\n幾年前 我地要真普選<br />\n呢個政府就比件垃圾我地<br />\n叫我地袋住先<br />\n<br />\n到今日 我地要五大訴求<br />\n呢個政府再次比啲垃圾我地<br />\n再叫我地袋住先<br />\n<br />\n我唔知大家身邊既人有無上當<br />\n但我相信各位仍然係知道<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n麻煩各位係自己既fb ig之類 提醒你地身邊既人<br />\n政府係到呃緊我地<br />\n幾年前 我地唔會袋住先<br />\n到今日 我地都唔會袋住先<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"a55e3bb5721fd98114226b9b6d6288d19d60df10","tid":1540254,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1eMWb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1eMWb7.png&h=6a3a8481&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d98121f4a1b4b649f318789ba041762978c11638","tid":1540254,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gpmb7iT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpmb7iT.png&h=a3658cee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1325a8e3257c5c2773498603364ef5a04312c373","tid":1540254,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3AwnSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3AwnSi.jpg&h=d0f99a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲想叫我地袋住先？<br />\n食屎啦你"},{"pid":"0ac6acc9654291f9b1aa8b8b2fafbc8856fd9c39","tid":1540254,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"09463d99ebd38753a05fbdb776615a1a75c7f83f","tid":154025